Constructor Detail

Submarine

public Submarine(OceanCanvas ocean,
                 ImageData imageData,
                 int y,
                 int amplitude,
                 double waveLenght,
                 double speed)
Create submarine with the given image, start coordinate, amplitude, wavelength (of the motion) and speed. The submarine enters the screen on the right hand side.

Parameters:
ocean - Ocean the submarine has to move in.
image - Image to be drawn.
y - Initial y coordinate.
amplitude - Amplitude of the sinus motion.
wavlength - Wave length of the sinus motion.
speed - Speed (x direction) of the submarine.
